When the screen is being drawn writes to VRAM are ignored, so that does sound like the issue you're having.<br /><br />If you want to be sure, you can configure BGB to jump into the debugger on invalid VRAM writes.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4826">adam_smasher</a> — Mon Aug 06, 2018 10:33 am</p><hr />
